title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: A small wheelbarrow has been left near a tall round haystack, a pitchfork laying prongs-down inside.  Beside the haystack is a paper sign pasted onto a board that is supported by a heavy post in the ground.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, south, southwest, west
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
